snippet.title: Chevelle - "Well Enough Alone" | Haider Ali (Guitar Cover) #Shorts
snippet.description:
“Well Enough Alone” by @CheVelle from the album Vena Sera — released in 2007 under @EpicRecords, and produced by Michael Baskette at Studio at the Palms in Paradise, NV, USA 
— guitar performance by @Haider Ali.

• Subscribe
https://www.youtube.com/haidertonight?sub_confirmation=1

• Thoughts
I clearly remember hearing this song for the first time in @WWE's Smackdown vs Raw (2008) game soundtrack, and saying to myself "man, this song is so damn heavy," and it forced me to check out @CheVelle, and it was the right decision to do so. I hope you guys dig this one.
